languages.text: "Я не питаю иллюзий — она редкостная дрянь, но я обещал ее родителям, что позабочусь о ней. Больше не смею задерживать Вашу Светлость".
"I have no illusions. She is a piece of work, but I promised her parents that I would take care of her. I dare not detain Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship} any longer."

languages.text: "Ich mache mir nichts vor. Sie ist eine harte Nuss, aber ich habe ihren Eltern versprochen, mich um sie zu kümmern. Ich möchte Eure {mf|Lordschaft|Ladyschaft} nicht länger behelligen."

languages.text: « Je ne me fais aucune illusion à son sujet. C'est une sale petite teigne, mais j'ai promis à ses parents de veiller sur elle. Sur ce, je m'en voudrais de vous retenir plus longtemps, Votre Seigneurie. »
languages.original_text: "I have no illusions. She is a piece of work, but I promised her parents that I would take care of her. I dare not detain Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship} any longer."

languages.text: «No me hago ilusiones. Es causa perdida, pero prometí a sus padres que cuidaría de ella. No le retendré más, mi{mf|lord|lady}».
languages.original_text: "I have no illusions. She is a piece of work, but I promised her parents that I would take care of her. I dare not detain Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship} any longer."

traits.locale_text: «No me hago ilusiones. Es causa perdida, pero prometí a sus padres que cuidaría de ella. No le retendré más, mi{mf|lord|lady}».

languages.text: 「夢想しているわけじゃありません。彼女は出来損ないですが、面倒を見ると彼女の両親に約束したのです。これ以上陛下をお引止めはいたしませんよ」
languages.original_text: "I have no illusions. She is a piece of work, but I promised her parents that I would take care of her. I dare not detain Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship} any longer."

languages.text: “我对她不抱幻想。她是个棘手的麻烦，但我答应过她的父母会好好照顾她。我不敢继续耽误您的时间了，大人。”
languages.original_text: "I have no illusions. She is a piece of work, but I promised her parents that I would take care of her. I dare not detain Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship} any longer."

languages.text: "Kuruntu yapmıyorum. Oldukça sıra dışı birisi ama ebeveynlerine ona göz kulak olacağıma dair söz verdim. {mf|Lord|Leydi} Hazretleri'ni daha fazla alıkoymaya kalkışmayacağım."
languages.original_text: "I have no illusions. She is a piece of work, but I promised her parents that I would take care of her. I dare not detain Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship} any longer."
